Tagline: Human persistence + AI scaffolding = Empowerment

What it is: LCES combines AI‚Äëpowered drafting with structured procedural education to produce safe, structured, docket‚Äëready, hearing‚Äëready, and appeal‚Äëready filings for people without lawyers.

